  <entry>
    <title>无重复字符的最长子串</title>
    <link href="https://ai-elaina.github.io/2021/04/16/LeetCode/hashMap/%E6%97%A0%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E9%95%BF%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%B2/"/>
    <id>https://ai-elaina.github.io/2021/04/16/LeetCode/hashMap/%E6%97%A0%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E9%95%BF%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%B2/</id>
    <published>2021-04-16T10:32:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-04-18T08:41:10.839Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="题目：无重复字符的最长子串"><a href="#题目：无重复字符的最长子串" class="headerlink" title="题目：无重复字符的最长子串"></a>题目：无重复字符的最长子串</h2><h3 id="要求："><a href="#要求：" class="headerlink" title="要求："></a>要求：</h3><p>​    给定一个字符串，请你找出其中不含有重复字符的 <strong>最长子串</strong> 的长度。</p><h3 id="提示："><a href="#提示：" class="headerlink" title="提示："></a>提示：</h3><p>​    <strong>·</strong> <code>0 &lt;= s.length &lt;= 5*10^4</code><br>​    <strong>·</strong> <code>s</code>有英文字母、数字、符号和空格组成</p><h3 id="题解："><a href="#题解：" class="headerlink" title="题解："></a>题解：</h3><p>​    <strong>方法一：滑动窗口法</strong><br>​        <strong>分析：</strong><br>​            <strong>·</strong> 我们可以用两个指针<code>l</code>与<code>r</code>分别代表着滑动窗口<strong>左边界</strong>和<strong>有边界</strong>。<br>​            <strong>·</strong> 在每步的操作中，我们都会把左指针向右移动<strong>一个</strong>，作为下一个子串的开始，然后开始不断移动右指针，保证子串中没有重复的字符，当遇到重复的字符时停止，并记录子串的长度。</p><p>​            <strong>·</strong> 当枚举结束后，找到的最长子串的长度即为答案。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">lengthOfLengestSubstring</span><span class="params">(String s)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Set&lt;Character&gt; occ = <span class="keyword">new</span> HashSet&lt;Character&gt;();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> n = s.length();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> r = <span class="number">0</span> <span class="comment">//右指针</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> res = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> l = <span class="number">0</span>; l &lt; n; ++l) &#123; <span class="comment">//l作为左指针</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (l != <span class="number">0</span>) &#123; <span class="comment">//当每次枚举会移除前一个元素</span></span><br><span class="line">occ.remove(l - <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (r &lt; n &amp;&amp; !occ.contains(r)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//不断移动右指针，并判断当前子串是否有重复字符</span></span><br><span class="line">occ.add(s.charAt(r)) <span class="comment">// 如果没有把当前字符加入哈希表</span></span><br><span class="line">++r;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">res = Math.max(res, r - i)<span class="comment">//r-i为当前无重复字符子串的长度。此时r指向第一个重复字符。</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> res;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​    <strong>缺点：</strong>我们每次一动作左指针都只是移动一个单位，此时会有很多不必要的循环。</p><img data-src="/../../source/images/%E6%97%A0%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E9%95%BF%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%B2/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720191127200959.jpg" style="zoom:50%;"><p>​        当我们遇到右指针第一个重复字符时，左指针一步一步向右移动</p><p><strong>方法一改进：</strong></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">lengthOfLongestSubstring</span><span class="params">(String s)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Map&lt;Character, Integer&gt; ooc = <span class="keyword">new</span> HashMap&lt;Character, Integer&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> n = s.length();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> res = <span class="number">0</span>, l = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> r = <span class="number">0</span>; r &lt; n; ++r) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">char</span> ch = s.charAt(r);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (ooc.containsKey(ch)) &#123; <span class="comment">//当遇到重复字符时，</span></span><br><span class="line">            l = Math.max(ooc.get(ch) + <span class="number">1</span>, l); <span class="comment">//左指针移到子串中重复字符的下一个 如果重复字符的下一个小于当前位置，则不改变，因为改变后子串中会有重复字符，左指针不可能向左移动。</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        res = Math.max(res, r - l + <span class="number">1</span>); <span class="comment">//因为移动了左指针，所以r不再是重复字符了，所以+1。</span></span><br><span class="line">        ooc.put(ch, r);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> res;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;题目：无重复字符的最长子串&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#题目：无重复字符的最长子串&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;题目：无重复字符的最长子串&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;题目：无重复字符的最长子串&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&quot;要求：&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#要求：&quot; c</summary>
      
    
    
    
